txt.en: Urshúlagar can be found in Emyn Duir.\n\nYou should defeat any evil Men you find at Urshúlagar.

The pass to Emyn Duir is watched by Easterling and Black Númenórean warriors loyal to Sauron. They should be defeated at the encampment of Urshúlagar, where they make their plans and carry out the strategies of the Dark Lord.
Urshúlagar can be found in Emyn Duir.\n\nYou should defeat evil Men at Urshúlagar.
Defeated many evil Men at Urshúlagar.
Under the command of Sauron, many evil Men gather at the encampment of Urshúlagar.
You defeated many Easterlings and Black Númenóreans at the watch post of Urshúlagar, helping to hinder some of their plans for the Shadowfells.
